short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Automatically loads Publishers pages through Warwick Library Proxy

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This will only work if you are a Student or Member of staff at the University of Warwick. This uses the Library's Pugwash proxy system which requires a login.

Library Proxy Information - https://warwick.ac.uk/services/library/find-resources/e-access/proxy/

Full code available at - https://github.com/keir-l/LibProxy
